## Additional Terms for Academic Use

This project is designed for educational purposes in econometrics and statistics.

### Citation

If you use this material in your academic work, please cite as:

```
Rodríguez, E. (2025). Econometrics Time Series: A Comprehensive Computational
Econometrics Framework. GitHub. https://github.com/emanuelquintana-glitch/Econometrics_time
```

### Data and References

- All data used in examples should be properly cited according to their original sources
- External packages and libraries retain their original licenses
- Statistical methodologies and algorithms referenced follow standard econometric literature

### Disclaimer

This educational material is provided for learning purposes. Users should:
- Verify all statistical results independently
- Consult original sources for critical applications
- Apply appropriate statistical rigor in research contexts
- Follow ethical guidelines in data analysis and reporting

